| pair               | {x, y} | set of two elements         |                                                       |

#### Algebra

| Name        | Symbol | Meaning                  | Notes                                                      |
| ----------- | ------ | ------------------------ | ---------------------------------------------------------- |
| zero        | 0      | zero                     |                                                            |
| add         | +      | add                      |                                                            |
| neg / sub | -      | negative or substraction | neg for the unary function, sub for the binary function |
